 />\n　汗水附纖維表面被細菌分解 <br />\n　理大紡織及製衣學系副教授簡志偉解釋﹕「聚酯纖維運動衣更易產生臭味，是因為聚酯纖維吸水性欠佳，汗水粒子僅能黏附在纖維表面，因此仍會被細菌分解，亦容易被我們嗅到；相反天然纖維具吸水特性，汗水及細菌製造的難聞化合物會被吸進天然纖維中，相比人造纖維，不易嗅到。」 <br />\n　有一些研究亦發現，某些細菌較易在聚酯纖維衣物上大量繁殖，卻較難在棉料上滋生。"},{"pid":"275555a0ddb6407fa3f6ca35f086c7351896d2de","tid":707586,"uid":115728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T21:25:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.chilin.hk/hk/?job=body&amp;sec=eJzbcGxpFAAGugJ2&amp;page=9&amp;path=Q29udGVudF9OZXdzLmNmbT9DaGFubmVsPWphJlBhdGg9MjAyMTA5NzEyNjA2L3ZtYTEuY2Zt&amp;pic=big&amp;date=20170630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.chilin.hk%2Fhk%2F%3Fjob%3Dbody%26sec%3DeJzbcGxpFAAGugJ2%26page%3D9%26path%3DQ29udGVudF9OZXdzLmNmbT9DaGFubmVsPWphJlBhdGg9MjAyMTA5NzEyNjA2L3ZtYTEuY2Zt%26pic%3Dbig%26date%3D20170630&d=rY9%2FuYhCWQaw6ZA0H4lBVpnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=83e78b01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.chilin.hk/hk/?job=body&amp;sec=eJzbcGxpFAAGugJ2&amp;page=9&amp;path=Q29udGVudF9OZXdzLmNmbT9DaGFubmVsPWphJlBhdGg9MjAyMTA5NzEyNjA2L3ZtYTEuY2Zt&amp;pic=big&amp;date=20170630</a>"}]}